The VDO gauges are available in metric. My '84 VW Rabbit (Golf) had them.

By the way you can install them in three 2" holes between the radio and 
ashtray.

Measure 4 or 5 times!!!

VERY stock looking.

I even removed the glass fronts and painted the needles white to match the 
speedo.

